The paper discusses the use of deep learning techniques for 3D object reconstruction from images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses network architectures and training mechanisms, which are relevant to the graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the reconstruction of specific object classes such as human body shapes and faces, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category.
